        "action": "Allow nut allergy sufferers into the UK Armed Forces",
        "additional_details": "Currently if he/she develop an allergy whilst in the armed forces he/she won\u2019t get medically removed but will have their tours shortened.\r\nI want the government to allow sufferers of any peanut/ nut allergy to join any of the UK forces PROVIDING they sign disclaimer in the event they may suffer an attack. Also if he/she can provide proof they haven\u2019t had to use an EpiPen in the last 2years.",
